4481	"He didn't like to be reminded that he was different because mentally he
4554	wasn't different," says Gianni Merlo, who co-authored Pistorius's book. "This
4632	was because of the way his mother brought him up as a kid. He has a spirit
4707	that is completely different because he was born that way. Without knowing
4782	what it feels like to be normal, you feel normal."
